    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Electronic components fabricated as a single unit, in which  transistors, diodes, capacitors and resistors are connected on a substrate of semiconductor material, typically silicon. These circuits may be as small as a few square millimeters. Individual circuit components are generally microscopic in size.</Note_Text>
